Type: Package
Package: sdmTMBextra
Title: Extra Functions for Working with 'sdmTMB' Models
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(c("Sean", "C."), "Anderson", , "sean@seananderson.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9563-1937"))
Description: Facilitates fitting 'sdmTMB' models with 'rstan'/'tmbstan';
    adding meshes with correlation barriers, and calculating 'DHARMa'
    residuals.  Accompanies the 'sdmTMB' package.
